{"tid":1290224,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【幫手反起底】父母搵仔女group嘅admin","createTime":"2019-07-06T12:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T16:39:20.000Z","uid":266415,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"304b640cad06744a9b63dbea919c3bf89f974e4b","tid":1290224,"uid":266415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k0HRw2i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk0HRw2i.jpg&h=5c6985fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#突發 #求幫手 最近幾日有個 tg group 以父母搵仔女嘅名義不停發放義士嘅相片同起佢哋底，最無恥嘅係，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">佢哋連一位透露有意輕生嘅女仔都唔放過，務求要逼死義士</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭先佢哋其中一位 admin 似乎將內部信息send錯落group，幾分鐘之後已經delete咗，好彩我哋cap定圖。<br />\n<br />\n睇佢哋行文用字似乎有啲似紀律部隊。我哋懇請各各位連登仔一齊集思廣益，務求將呢班禽獸起底，一網打盡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17f22f3e24e625770d848636e4f31b4960f0c5db","tid":1290224,"uid":274896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:03:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de7a5c4b784ae0c0696c5d705908a3e42c37fa83","tid":1290224,"uid":271601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:04:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1253036895d9a29b8f4225a82d3c54016b76ef56","tid":1290224,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0556f70668ee8d23d799a54bea1af7d1d97240c","tid":1290224,"uid":71216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:05:46.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"f28460af75ca02d7219a3901089baa71fd933a29","tid":1290224,"uid":71216,"like":0,"disli